      <p class="text-[#D4A853] font-mono text-sm tracking-widest mb-4">LEADERSHIP</p>
      <h2 class="font-['DM_Serif_Display'] text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-[#1A1A2E]">
        Meet Our <span class="text-gold-gradient">Chairman</span>
      </h2>
